title: A Review of Episode 1215 Ben O’Brian
description:
Ben is a hunter, podcaster and works on the show Meat Eater. He’s a great guy to listen to and someone that represents the world of hunting in a very articulate way. His conversation with Joe was very funny and educational in respects to hunting. Make sure to check it out!

Enjoy my review folks!
